== Mubisi bya huye ==
[[Dosiye:UMUSOZI_WA_HUYE_(_HUYE_MOUNTAIN).jpg|thumb|UMUSOZI WA HUYE ]]
[[File:Ibisi bya Huye.jpg|thumb|Ibisi bya Huye]]
ibisi bya [[Akarere ka Huye|Huye]] ubu biherereye muntara ya amajyepko mu [[Akarere ka Huye|karere ka  Huye]]

ni umusozi wavuzwe cyane mu mateka yu [[Rwanda]] kuko uvugwaho umukecuru

wahimbwe akazina ka Nyagakecuru bivugwako yari yarigometse ku Mwami

uyu Nyagakecuru ya menyekanye cyane ku Ngoma yu umwami Ruganzu wa II Ndori<ref>https://www.gasabo.net/2019/11/19/menya-mu-bisi-bya-huye-kwa-nyagakecuru/</ref>

== Amateka ==
amateka atubwirako mu bisi bya Huye hatari mu [[Rwanda Rwacu|Rwanda]] akaba ariyo mpamvu

kungoma yu [[Umwami|Umwami Ruganzu II Ndoli]] yifashishije ingabo ze zitwaga [[Igihugu|ibisumizi]]

bakajya gutera kugirango bigarurire ako gace kari gatuyeho uwo Nyagakecuru

wari warigometse ku Mwami<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/ubukerarugendo/ahantu/Ibisi-bya-Huye-bigiye-kugirwa-ahantu-nyaburanga</ref>

== ibisobanuro ==
ubusanzwe ibisi bisobanura uruhererekane rwi imisozi miremire ituye ahantu

== Aho biherereye ==
ibisi bya huye biherereye mu murenge wa huye akarere ka Huye

mu Ntara ya Amajyepfo mu kagari ka Sovu<ref>https://bwiza.com/?Ese-Ibisi-bya-Huye-bisobanuye-iki-Nyagakecuru-wahavugwaga-we-yari-muntu-ki</ref>
